Record Point has x: i32; y: i32.

Union MaybePoint has none; some point: Point.

Type Position be Point.

Type OptionalPosition be MaybePoint.

To score maybe maybe: OptionalPosition, giving i32.
Give match maybe:
MaybePoint.some with point gives point.x plus point.y;
otherwise gives 0.

To main, giving i32.
Let p: Position be Point with x be 3 and y be 4.
Give score maybe MaybePoint.some with point be p.
